{"tid":1723601,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【龍來了】中原八大樓價指數齊升　CCL按周升1.51%　升幅29周最大","createTime":"2019-11-15T08:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T08:44:18.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8b8f8c6a15f0e4670e0ca1af050ee4818ce422b9","tid":1723601,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:39:26.000Z","msg":"中原城市領先指數CCL最新報182.1點，按周升1.51%，升幅為29周最大。中原城市大型屋苑領先指數CCL Mass報183.66點，按周升1.8%，升幅為84周最大。CCL（中小型單位）報182.28點，按周升1.77%，升幅同為84周最大。三大整體指數齊升2周，CCL_Mass累升2.18%、CCL（中小型單位）累升2.04%及CCL累升1.73%。<br />\nCCL（大型單位）報181.19點，按周升0.2%，結束連跌2周。豪宅樓價近5周持續在180點左右窄幅徘徊。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產研究部高級聯席董事黃良昇指出，今周CCL八大指數齊升，為32周後首現，上一次出現是今年3月份，當時正處於樓價上升階段。政府調高按揭保險樓價上限後，三大整體指數連升2周，兼今周升幅明顯擴大。CCL_Mass升1.80%、CCL（中小型單位）升1.77%及CCL升1.51%。<br />\n<br />\n本周四區樓價齊升<br />\n本周四區樓價齊升，為32周以來首現。當中新界西樓價升幅持續顯著，帶領大市止跌回升。新界西CCL_Mass報166.23點，按周升1.64%，連升2周共3.04%。<br />\n<br />\n港島CCL_Mass報190.83點，按周升3.15%，升幅為19周最大，連升2周共3.41%。九龍CCL_Mass報178.75點，按周升1.31%，升幅為25周最大，連升2周共1.67%。新界東CCL_Mass報191.68點，結束4周連跌，按周升0.88%。"},{"pid":"470c89b590e726bb34fd3656786827f7636bc5b3","tid":1723601,"uid":69943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:42:14.000Z","msg":"宜家接火棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27208d1d730fe328db9fb3d5e224cd4d193484fe","tid":1723601,"uid":184103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"470c89b590e726bb34fd3656786827f7636bc5b3","tid":1723601,"uid":69943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:42:14.000Z","msg":"宜家接火棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:42:39.000Z","msg":"都講左10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0215f58c4d0d5aaff33d81360449085c2c83e28f","tid":1723601,"uid":165012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:43:38.000Z","msg":"按周升1.51%，升幅為29周最大<br />\n真係好大既升幅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb547c0a7e56655e2107d146d42c14043f0159a3","tid":1723601,"uid":256812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:43:38.000Z","msg":"咁都信？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38587ed8418cd0d643d1ff23196503822539653","tid":1723601,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kucJbpj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkucJbpj.png&h=43ac93ed&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}